# Emacs-like window handling
#
bind ^Xo next_window
bind ^X0 parse window kill
bind ^X1 parse window kill_others
bind ^X2 parse window new
bind ^X= parse window balance
bind ^X+ parse window grow 1
bind ^X- parse window shrink 1
bind ^Xz parse window grow 1
bind ^X^z parse window shrink 1
# bind ^X^ parse window grow 1
# bind ^X^^ parse window grow 1
